13:32.145 --> 13:33.780
* NO CONTROL *

13:33.847 --> 13:35.248
* NO CON-TROL *

13:35.315 --> 13:39.086
* DRINK YOUR CONSCIENCE
TO FEEL YOUR SOUL *

13:44.224 --> 13:45.926
* REFLECT THE LIE *

13:45.993 --> 13:47.694
* CHANGE THE LIGHT *

13:47.760 --> 13:50.530
* THERE ARE ALWAYS
2 SIDES *

13:50.597 --> 13:52.032
* TOO MANY SHADOWS *

13:52.099 --> 13:53.700
